    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Mesh-building helpers shared between the rubberband and feature highlight geometries. Each helper appends to a raw vertex/index buffer using a fixed 10-float vertex layout: position(3) + normal(3) + rgba(4). </para>
    </detaileddescription>
